#Privacy Policy for ShravaniMela 

Effective Date: 27/06/2026 
 Last Updated: 27/06/2006 

This Privacy Policy describes how ShravaniMela app collects, uses, and protects the information of users when using our Android mobile application. 

 

1. Information We Collect 

We collect the following types of data only with your consent and solely for enabling app functionality: 

a. Camera Access 

Used to capture photos through the app for features such as uploading images in the contest photo of the day. 

We do not store or share photos without your consent. 

b. Storage Access 

Required to upload or view media files within the app. 

Files are temporarily used to complete user-requested actions (like upload). 

c. Location Access 

Used to provide services like navigation, showing nearby places. 

We do not track your real-time location or store location history. 

 d. Microphone access 

Used to allow users to search the nearby facilities based on their location. 

2. How We Use Your Data 

We use your data only to enable features of the app, such as: 

Accessing your camera to take pictures. 

Uploading and viewing photos. 

Using your location for maps, navigation, and location-based features. 

We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data to third parties. 

 

3. Data Retention 

We retain only the necessary data as long as it's required to provide services. Uploaded files may be stored in a secure cloud database if your action (like submitting a photo) requires it. 

 

4. Third-Party Services 

The app may use third-party services like: 

Supabase to store user data and provide real-time features. 
 Each third-party provider has its own privacy policy. 

 

5. Your Rights 

You can: 

Deny camera or location access at any time in device settings. 

Request deletion of your data by contacting us. 

 

6. Security 

We take reasonable steps to protect your data from unauthorized access or misuse. However, no method is 100% secure. 

 

7. Childrenâ€™s Privacy 

This app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect data from them. 

 

8. Changes to This Policy 

We may update this policy from time to time. You will be notified via app update or on our website. 

 

